  li.checklist__item
    +svg('checkmark', ['checklist__item__icon', 'icon-svg'])
    .checklist__item__content
      :markdown
        Do not use more than 5 options in a segmented control. A <a href="./dropdown.html" class="link">dropdown</a> can be an alternative.

